t System (CRM)\"<|>\"concepts\"<|>\"A Customer Relationship Management System (CRM) records the relationship between the enterprise and its customers, managing interactions and data throughout the customer lifecycle.\")##\n\n(\"entity\"<|>\"Operational Decision\"<|>\"concepts\"<|>\"An operational decision relates to the day-to-day running of the business, such as reordering inventory when levels reach a certain point.\")##\n\n(\"entity\"<|>\"Executive Information System (EIS)\"<|>\"concepts\"<|>\"An Executive Information System (EIS) provides summarized information to executives of an organization, often including features like data visualizations and reporting tools.\")##\n\n(\"entity\"<|>\"Data Visualizations\"<|>\"features\"<|>\"Data visualizations include various graphical representations of data such as bar charts, line charts, pie charts, and tables. They help in understanding and analyzing data trends and patterns.\")##\n\n(\"entity\"<|>\"Monthly Sales Data\"<|>\"features\"<|>\"Monthly sales data for all ten stores over a year can be visualized using a table to show detailed numerical information.\")##\n\n(\"entity\"<|>\"Quarterly Sales Data\"<|>\"features\"<|>\"Quarterly sales data for the Bigton stores over a year can be visualized using a compound bar chart to show multiple data series over multiple periods.\")##\n\n(\"entity\"<|>\"Total Sales Data\"<|>\"features\"<|>\"Total sales data for each of the Bigton stores for a month can be visualized using a simple bar chart to present a single data series over multiple periods.\")##\n\n(\"entity\"<|>\"Proportion of Revenue Data\"<|>\"features\"<|>\"The proportion of revenue earned by each product category for a month can be visualized using a pie chart to show the proportions for a single period.\")##\n\n**Relationships:**\n\n(\"relationship\"<|>\"Implementation and Evaluation of EPOS and ERPS in XYZ Stores\"<|>\"Electronic Point of Sale (EPOS)\"<|>\"The case of Implementation and Evaluation of EPOS and ERPS in